code: import axios from"axios";var API_URL="http://localhost:3001/api/v1/exercises/";var ExerciseService={getExerciseHistory:function getExerciseHistory(){return axios.get(API_URL);},createExercise:function createExercise(exercise){return axios.post(API_URL,exercise);},updateExercise:function updateExercise(exerciseId,exercise){return axios.put("".concat(API_URL).concat(exerciseId),exercise);},deleteExercise:function deleteExercise(exerciseId){return axios.delete("".concat(API_URL).concat(exerciseId));}};export default ExerciseService;
